parameters: セギ裸2
face01
Actor2_7
\N<Rame>Segi-san... please tell me. How long will this continue...?
\N<Segi>Rame-chan...

\N<Rame>Even though you're his... his wife, to be dressed like
that...
\N<Segi>...
\N<Rame>And with your belly so big... why don't you ask him to stop?
\N<Rame>It's all his orders that we have to do this, isn't it...?

\N<Segi>Yes... I think maybe he's waiting for us to come to him for
help.

\N<Segi>He said he was a seeker of strength that could be gained
through love... but that's not true. I can tell, having
watched him closely...

\N<Segi>Once he obtained a false love from me and gained power, he
then wanted the respect of his subordinates.

\N<Segi>He's neither a strong man nor a seeker. He's just a common
man who, once he gets one thing, craves for the next.
\N<Rame>Segi-san...

\N<Segi>That's why, I guess, I don't want to be exactly as he
wishes. It might be a meaningless stubbornness, though.
\N<Rame>...

\N<Rame>I've been toyed with by him for so long. I think... I was
foolish.

\N<Rame>Causing trouble for many people... and hurting the most
important person to me.

\N<Rame>It's all... too late now, but... if I could go back in time,
I would...
\N<Segi>It's not too late. You are still young.

\N<Segi>I may have failed, but you, Rame-chan, still have plenty of
time to regain what you've lost.
\N<Rame>Don't you think about escaping from here, Segi-san?

\N<Segi>Yes... I've thought about it many times. There were even
times when I acted on it. But... with this body, I can't go
back to Lord Yuia now.
\N<Rame>...

\N<Segi>It's possible that I hate Rozaro... that man. But that
doesn't mean I have the right to love Lord Yuia again.
\N<Segi>To that extent... I have changed from who I was before...

\N<Segi>All I can do is pray that the person I loved can live out
his life safely...

\N<Segi>And then... to give birth to this innocent child and protect
it with all my might.
\N<Rame>Segi-san...
\N<Luda Soldier>Yo, mind if I interrupt?
\N<Rame>Eh?! Wha... what...?!
\N<Segi>Get out...! What do you want here...?!

\N<Luda Soldier>You sure you should be talking like that? If you don't
listen to us, you'll surely regret it.
\N<Segi>What did you say...?!

\N<Luda Soldier>Hey, captain's wife? It's about your dear son's life at
stake here, you know?
\N<Rame>Ri-Riia-chan...?!
\N<Segi>Don't tell me... you've taken Riia as a hostage...?!

\N<Luda Soldier>Well, who knows. What's certain is, if you keep up that
defiant attitude, you won't know what might happen to your
cute son.
\N<Segi>Coward... Have some shame!

\N<Luda Soldier>Heh heh, got it now? If you understand, then you better
quietly listen to what we say.
A
